name: あさひ
text:
最初のステップのキレ……？
それともサビ前の振り……？
trans:
Was it the execution of the first step...?
Or the choreo just before the chorus...?

name: あさひ
text:
いや……それだけじゃ……
表情……？　魅せ方……？
trans:
No... Can't be just those...
Facial expression...? Presentation...?

name: プロデューサー
text:
あさひ、気持ちはわかる
俺も悔しいが、とにかく今は戻ろう
trans:
I understand your feelings, Asahi.
I'm also frustrated, but for now, let's go back.
